    <p>KELLY: That's DNI Jim Clapper speaking yesterday in remarks clearly that he wants policymaker number one to hear. And yesterday Trump himself seemed to walk back some of his earlier criticism. He was tweeting about intelligence. But he said he's a big fan.</p>
    <p>GREENE: He's saying he's a big fan of the intelligence community.</p>
    <p>KELLY: That's what he says.</p>
