    <p>Republican Senator Jeff Flake of Arizona joins us now on the line. Senator, thanks for being with us.</p>
    <p>JEFF FLAKE: Hey, thanks for having me on.</p>
    <p>MARTIN: Let's start with these unverified documents alleging links between Donald Trump and Russia. Have you seen them?</p>
