    <p>(LAUGHTER)</p>
    <p>SIMON: William Peter Blatty has just brought out a new and expanded revised version of his mammoth bestseller "The Exorcist," the 40th anniversary edition. Thanks so much.</p>
    <p>BLATTY: Oh, my. Thank you very much, Scott. My pleasure.</p>
