    <p>GREENE: And she is excited about tomorrow's inauguration. She almost got to go.</p>
    <p>LINDA CAUDILL: Kind of late in the game, I got invitations. But I did not get them until about a week ago. And at that point in time, it was not possible to get a flight. They were all booked.</p>
