    <p>Tom, thanks so much for being with us.</p>
    <p>TOM GOLDMAN, BYLINE: My pleasure, Scott.</p>
    <p>SIMON: There's been a fair amount of division in American sport over President Trump, hasn't there? Ranging in LeBron James, Kareem Abdul-Jabbar, on the one hand...</p>
