    <p>UNIDENTIFIED CHOIR: (Singing) (Unintelligible).</p>
    <p>SIMON: It was an ecumenical service, which featured prayers from Christians, Muslims, Jews and Hindus, among others. This, of course, is President Trump's first full day in office. And he has already signed an executive order related to the Affordable Care Act. NPR's Scott Horsley joins us.</p>
    <p>Scott, thanks for being with us.</p>
