    <p>(CHEERING)</p>
    <p>SIEGLER: Houston is known for its large immigrant and refugee population. Rabbi Josh Lobel (ph) came out with his family to a protest downtown to show support for refugees fleeing war zones and to protest the temporary travel ban.</p>
    <p>JOSH LOBEL: You know, people who are just looking to escape, that, to me, is a terrifying sign.</p>
    <p>UNIDENTIFIED PROTESTERS: (Chanting, unintelligible).</p>
